*mythgallery-0.11 (18 Aug 2003)

  18 Aug 2003; Max Kalika <max@gentoo.org> mythgallery-0.11.ebuild:
  Bump version to 0.11. Change make install to einstall.

  07 Aug 2003; Max Kalika <max@gentoo.org> mythgallery-0.10.ebuild:
  Depend on either mythtv or mythfrontend.

  03 Jul 2003; Max Kalika <max@gentoo.org> mythgallery-0.8.ebuild:
  Set KEYWORDS to ~x86.

*mythgallery-0.10 (01 Jul 2003)

  01 Jul 2003; Max Kalika <max@gentoo.org> mythgallery-0.10.ebuild:
  Bump version to 0.10. Drop installation of mythgaller-settings.txt as it is no
  longer needed. Add similar note as mythtv regarding the importance of keeping
  database up to date between upgrades.

  22 Jun 2003; Max Kalika <max@gentoo.org> mythgallery-0.9.ebuild:
  Cleanup and consistancy: depend on sed-4, die if sed fails. Drop unused
  myconf setting.

  18 Jun 2003; Max Kalika <max@gentoo.org> mythgallery-0.9.ebuild:
  Change depend to media-tv/mythtv.

*mythgallery-0.9 (09 Jun 2003)

  09 Jun 2003; Max Kalika <max@gentoo.org> mythgallery-0.9.ebuild:
  Bump to 0.9.  Make all sed operations inline.  Move config file into
  /etc/mythtv for consistancy and CONFIG_PROTECT support.

*mythgallery-0.8 (27 Mar 2003)

  26 Mar 2003; Max Kalika <max@gentoo.org> mythgallery-0.9.ebuild:
  Initial import.
